```json
{
"application": "GrADS",
"software": [
"GrADS",
"prod_util",
"prod_envir",
"grib_util",
"wgrib",
"wgrib2"
],
"resources": [
"/apps/test/lmodules/core/",
"/apps/test/grads/spack/opt/spack/cray-sles15-zen2/gcc-11.2.0/grads-2.2.2-wckmyzg7qh5smosf6och6ehqtqlxoy4f/data/udpt",
"/apps/test/grads/spack/opt/spack/cray-sles15-zen2/gcc-11.2.0/grads-2.2.2-wckmyzg7qh5smosf6och6ehqtqlxoy4f/data",
"/apps/ops/prod/libs/intel/19.1.3.304/grib_util/1.2.2/bin/wgrib",
"/apps/ops/prod/libs/intel/19.1.3.304/wgrib2/2.0.8/bin/wgrib2",
"/lfs/h1/ops/prod/com/aqm/v6.1/cs.${NOW}",
"/lfs/h2/emc/physics/noscrub/${USER}/com/aqm/${exp}/cs.${NOW}",
"/lfs/h1/ops/para/com/aqm/v6.1/cs.${NOW}",
"/lfs/h2/emc/ptmp/${USER}/com/aqm/${exp}/cs.${NOW}",
"/lfs/h2/emc/physics/noscrub/${USER}/com/aqm/${exp}/cs.${NOW}",
"/lfs/h2/emc/physics/noscrub/${USER}/com/aqm/para6/cs.${NOW}",
"/lfs/h2/emc/physics/noscrub/${USER}/com/aqm/para99/cs.${NOW}",
"/lfs/h2/emc/physics/noscrub/${USER}/com/aqm/arlv6/cs.${NOW}",
"/lfs/h2/emc/ptmp/Jianping.Huang/com/aqm/para13/cs.${NOW}",
"/lfs/h2/emc/physics/noscrub/${USER}/com/aqm/${exp}/cs.${NOW}",
"/lfs/h2/emc/stmp/${USER}/com2_aqm_${exp}_${mfileid}_max.${NOW}${cych}",
"/lfs/h2/emc/stmp/${USER}/daily_plot_${mfileid}/aqm_${plotexp}_o3",
"/lfs/h2/emc/stmp/${USER}/job_submit",
"/lfs/h2/emc/ptmp/${USER}/batch_logs"
]
}
```

This script is primarily running under **GrADS**, a graphical data analysis and visualization system. It uses several other modules and libraries:

* **prod_util:** Provides utilities for production environment.
* **prod_envir:** Sets up the production environment.
* **grib_util:** Handles GRIB format data.
* **wgrib:**  A GRIB data manipulation tool.
* **wgrib2:** Another GRIB data manipulation tool.

The script also relies on various directories and files located in specific locations on the system. These include:

* **/apps/test/lmodules/core/:**  A directory containing modules.
* **/apps/test/grads/spack/opt/spack/cray-sles15-zen2/gcc-11.2.0/grads-2.2.2-wckmyzg7qh5smosf6och6ehqtqlxoy4f/data/udpt:**  The directory for GrADS user defined parameter tables (UDPT).
* **/apps/test/grads/spack/opt/spack/cray-sles15-zen2/gcc-11.2.0/grads-2.2.2-wckmyzg7qh5smosf6och6ehqtqlxoy4f/data:**  The directory for GrADS data.
* **/apps/ops/prod/libs/intel/19.1.3.304/grib_util/1.2.2/bin/wgrib:** The path to the `wgrib` executable.
* **/apps/ops/prod/libs/intel/19.1.3.304/wgrib2/2.0.8/bin/wgrib2:** The path to the `wgrib2` executable.
* **/lfs/h1/ops/prod/com/aqm/v6.1/cs.${NOW}:** The directory containing the AQM data (production).
* **/lfs/h2/emc/physics/noscrub/${USER}/com/aqm/${exp}/cs.${NOW}:** The directory containing the AQM data (user specific).
* **/lfs/h1/ops/para/com/aqm/v6.1/cs.${NOW}:** The directory containing the AQM data (parallel run).
* **/lfs/h2/emc/ptmp/${USER}/com/aqm/${exp}/cs.${NOW}:** Another directory containing the AQM data (user specific).
* **/lfs/h2/emc/physics/noscrub/${USER}/com/aqm/para6/cs.${NOW}:**  Another directory containing the AQM data (parallel run).
* **/lfs/h2/emc/physics/noscrub/${USER}/com/aqm/para99/cs.${NOW}:** Another directory containing the AQM data (parallel run).
* **/lfs/h2/emc/physics/noscrub/${USER}/com/aqm/arlv6/cs.${NOW}:** Another directory containing the AQM data (parallel run).
* **/lfs/h2/emc/ptmp/Jianping.Huang/com/aqm/para13/cs.${NOW}:** Another directory containing the AQM data (user specific).
* **/lfs/h2/emc/physics/noscrub/${USER}/com/aqm/${exp}/cs.${NOW}:** Another directory containing the AQM data (user specific).
* **/lfs/h2/emc/stmp/${USER}/com2_aqm_${exp}_${mfileid}_max.${NOW}${cych}:** A temporary directory used by the script.
* **/lfs/h2/emc/stmp/${USER}/daily_plot_${mfileid}/aqm_${plotexp}_o3:** The directory where the plots are stored.
* **/lfs/h2/emc/stmp/${USER}/job_submit:** A directory for submitting jobs.
* **/lfs/h2/emc/ptmp/${USER}/batch_logs:**  The directory where batch job logs are stored.

These directories and files are accessed and used by the script to process the data, create plots, and manage the workflow.
